    "updated_at": "2017-03-22T15:31:49Z",
    "body": "Same issue here.\r\n\r\nI can confirm that setting the window to fullscreen after the domready event solves the issue. For meteor-desktop as follows:\r\n\r\n        eventsBus.on('windowCreated', (window) => {\r\n            window.webContents.on('dom-ready', () => {\r\n              window.setFullScreen(true);\r\n            });\r\n        });"
  },
